            <div type="transcript" id="J106">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Daisy follows soft the Sun --</l>
                    <l>And when his golden walk is done --</l>
                    <l>Sits shily at his feet --</l>
                    <l>He -- waking -- finds the flower there --</l>
                    <l>Wherefore -- Marauder -- art thou here?</l>
                    <l>Because, Sir, love is sweet!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We are the Flower -- Thou the Sun!</l>
                    <l>Forgive us, if as days decline --</l>
                    <l>We nearer steal to Thee!</l>
                    <l>Enamored of the parting West --</l>
                    <l>The peace -- the flight -- the Amethyst --</l>
                    <l>Night's possibility!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
